- request class handle form inputs or request body
- response class handle response format specially for apis
- database class to handle operations in multi drivers database (database manager)
- validation class
- full authentication module for web and api with views
- exceptions class to handle errors and report it with friendly views
- collection class to deal with models
- str class for string operations
- migrations module with cli
- simple orm
- simple query builder
- handle views for front end and backend
- advanced middlewares
- mail class for mailing
- make cli to make new controller - model - route - views and crud operations
- make crud directly (full api with routes )after make:crud generator in cli